members.name: resizeObserver
members.default: new ResizeObserver((entries) => { for (const entry of entries) { // Made by chatGPT so that the text is inside the wrapper this.maxContainerWidth = -125.36 + 3.79 * entry.contentRect.height; this.containerWidth = Math.min( entry.contentRect.width, this.maxContainerWidth ); } })
